				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Finders Creeperz" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>&amp;quot;Finders Creeperz&amp;quot; is a uniquely clever and challenging game that requires a combination of strategy, luck and killer instinct.  A plethora of different gameplay scenarios will unfold giving a different outcome every time and fun for all of the family. The aim of the game is to trick and capture your opponents with the help of your CREEPER, action cards and traps (pre-game traps and on board traps) leaving you in the clear to get around the board and take the win. It's high paced from start to finish and you can be called in to action on anyone's turn. Just because your go is done, you are most certainly not safe. The attack/question cards are hectic and full of twists. Those who you think are your friends often turn out to be enemies and you are all but guaranteed to have to choose between one friend or another. We take no responsibility for any arguments that follow. Do you trap your kid or let your partner win? Will you put yourself in a trap just to send your best friend back to the start? OF COURSE YOU WILL! Be ruthless. Be bold.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Yes, we know that the vast majority of games claim to be equally as fun for parents as it is for kids but this one actually is... Trust me, as a parent there is little I enjoy more than the look on a kid's face go from joy and smugness when they think they are going to win, to despair and anger when they slowly realise they most certainly are not. It's like a fun punishment. &amp;quot;Funishment,&amp;quot; if you will... After all, they'd most certainly do it to you! Life isn't fair and they will soon realise this.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
